for the time being.

294
00:21:25,149 --> 00:21:26,816
Day classes are canceled.

295
00:21:26,849 --> 00:21:29,349
Make sure you don't
let anyone outside.

296
00:21:29,383 --> 00:21:33,649
-Hey, Ruka, are you all right?

297
00:21:33,683 --> 00:21:38,283
-I want to be able
to show him that I

